Features:
- ICAP request mode
- ICAP response mode
- Shadow service
- Preview bytes
- Supports multiple services (ClamAV, Cloudmersive and Virustotal)
- Responses with blick page incase of unsafe file
- Supports adding specific extensions to be processed
- Supports adding specific extensions to be bypassed
- Supports adding specific extensions to be rejected
- Supports setting maximum size to the body of the HTTP message 

Known issues: 
- Logs
- Block page in request mode
- Sending file with zero bytes while preview bytes is greater than zero
